    <div class="cover-sub">Why India's Relative Delay in AI Adoption May Become a Strategic Economic Strength</div>
    <p class="cover-subtitle">The prevailing narrative assumes first movers capture the most value from AI. History suggests the story is more nuanced — and potentially more interesting for India.</p>
